aPlusContent.title: From the manufacturer
aPlusContent.rawText:
From the manufacturer
Marcy Two Piece Olympic Weight Bench with Leg Developer and Squat Rack 
Looking to increase overall body strength and lean muscle mass while increasing your metabolic rate to burn calories? The Marcy MD-879 is your solution. The unique two-piece bench design allows you to utilize the upright bar support for squats and lunges, while the bench doubles as a stand-alone utility bench for lower leg, abdominal and bicep exercises. This bench features fully adjustable back pad for incline, decline and flat chest press exercises. With contoured foam roller pads that support form, you can get a total leg workout. The adjustable barbell crutches allows you to easily change the height of bar to conform to your workout needs. The built-in post on the machine conveniently organizes and stores weight plates. Included is an adjustable preacher curl pad with detachable bicep curl bar that allows extended bicep workouts. This all-in-one set is an ideal choice for any level user looking to building, toning and maintaining muscle mass. 
Adjustability 
The Marcy Two-Piece Olympic Bench MD-879 is adjustable at several points for your convenience. Adjust the back pad to decline, flat, and incline angles to change up your workout. And, the barbell catch / squat rack and adjustable curl pad are height adjustable for your comfort. 
Separate Bench and Bar Catch / Squat Rack 
Unlike many Olympic benches, the MD-879 barbell catch / squat rack is not attached to the bench. Simply move the bench away from the barbell catch to use it as a squat rack. 
Included Storage Space for Weight Plates 
For added convenience, the MD-879 Olympic Bench barbell catch has two Olympic pegs to store your weight plates and avoid cluttering your workout space. 
Preacher Curls with Preacher Curl Pad and Curl Handle 
Use the preacher curl pad and curl handle for preacher curls. Preacher curls take better aim at your biceps than regular curls. 
Leg Extensions with Leg Developer 
The included leg developer provides the option to do leg curls and leg extensions. Leg extensions are great for working out your quadriceps 
Incline Bench Exercises – Incline Presses 
With multiple backpad positions, the MD-879 provides a wide array of angles to pinpoint specific muscles. Incline Bench Presses target your chest muscles as presses do, however, the incline bench press focuses more on your upper chest muscles.

Product Description
Enhance your lower body workouts with DMoose Ankle Straps. Target glutes, hamstrings, and quads with secure, comfortable support for maximum results. 
8mm Neoprene Padding 
Provides supreme comfort, reducing discomfort for longer, more effective workouts. 
Anti-Rust D-Rings 
Stay rust-free for durability and longevity, ensuring lasting performance. 
Reinforced Stitching 
Increases strap strength, ready for heavy, frequent use without wearing out. 
Secure Hook & Loop 
Ensures a snug fit, keeping straps in place for safe, focused exercise. 
Achieve optimal muscle engagement during glute workouts, leg curls, and beyond with DMoose Ankle Straps, designed for maximum support and comfort. 
Previous page
Target and strengthen your glutes and hamstrings effectively with secure ankle attachment. 
Enhanced stability and a wider range of motion during workouts, adjustable and comfortable fit. 
Perform a variety of cable exercises, from glute kickbacks to leg curls, expanding your workout. 
Enjoy long-lasting use and comfort with high-quality materials and padded ankle cuffs. 
Next page
1 Isolate Glutes & Hams 2 Boost Stability & Motion 3 Versatile Exercise Option 4 Durable & Comfortable 
What exercises can I do with DMoose Ankle Straps? 
DMoose Ankle Straps unlock a world of leg and glute-focused exercises, including glute kickbacks, cable leg extensions, hamstring curls, inner/outer thigh exercises, hip abductions, and more 
How do I adjust the fit of the Ankle Straps? 
The industrial-strength hook-and-loop system allows for a secure and fully customizable fit. Simply fasten the strap around your ankle and adjust for the perfect level of snugness. 
Are these straps comfortable to use? 
Absolutely! The thick neoprene padding provides superior comfort during workouts, preventing chafing or discomfort even during intense exercises. 
How durable are DMoose Ankle Straps? 
They're built to last! The combination of high-quality nylon reinforced stitching, and powder-coated D-rings ensures these straps can handle even your toughest leg days. 
Can I use these straps with any cable machine? 
Yes! DMoose Ankle Straps are designed for standard cable machines, making them a versatile addition to your home or gym workout routine.

Yes, the Titan leg extension and leg curl machine promotes progressive overload with a plate-loaded system designed for use with Olympic-sized weight plates.

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
Why sissy squat machine is so great, and you should seriously consider to have one? 
If you're looking for a space-saving machine that will help you work your glutes, quads, and core, look no further than the sissy squat machine. Don't let the cowardly name fool you, this challenging machine is a fundamental tool for improving lower body muscle mass. While standing squats are one of the most underrated and easily neglected exercises, this machine helps athletes to achieve the greatest possible results by performing them regularly. 
Sissy squats work a variety of muscles, but none get more attention than the quadriceps. Accordingly, this exercise helps to balance your anterior and posterior chain muscles. The sissy squat machine helps to create an isolated environment where you can work the large muscles at the front of the thigh without overexerting your knees. 
Sissy squat machine also helps to promote full body balance and improve your core strength. 
Specifications 
Name:Deep Sissy Squat Workout Station(Multi-function)
Model:GM8300
Materials:Steel frame,PP Foam,PU leather
Installation Size:43.3x21.7x31.7 Inches
Max Weight Capacity:330lbs
Net/Gross:26lbs/30.6lbs
Key Features 
Extremely versatile, Deep sissy squat, band squat, hyper-extension (back extension), side extension, forward lunge, sit-up, push-up and even more. 
This product is foldable and movable,it is easy to move and store. 
Length,height,angle and padded foot holder all can be adjustable. 
Demonstrations 
Look straight ahead, maintaining normal angle of cervical and cervical vertebra, back uprightly,put up your chest and abdome,button tightening, keep your knees at right angles while squatting, and don't move forward excessively, the center of gravity is on the sole of the foot, split your feet as wide as your shoulder. 
Squat I and climb up both hands to the chest, and gaze to the front when you sit down! Move as far back as you can, and keep your knees and thighs at right angles. 
Straighten your waist to your leg support while holding your legs up slowly. Raise your upper body down.

Why you need TT2S leg extension and curl machine for leg day? 
“Pro"-is the answer. GMWD was shuttled to countless gyms and factories and tested it for over six months. If you want to get more sturdy thighs the right way, choose it. 
What's the latest update point of TT2S? 
GMWD's engineers have changed the way weight holder is attached. Once again, the weighing capacity is increased and structural stability also level up. It's one step closer to the perfect leg day training machine. 
What is the most memorable point in TT2S's design process? 
In order to simultaneously achieve good support for the knees, keep the axis of motion parallel to the knees, and make the equipment accessible to most family members in home gym, engineers has tweaked the statistics for over 1 month. 
Why you should do leg extension and leg curl at home? 
The leg extension and the leg curl are valuable isolation exercises. Leg curls are a valuable addition to your leg-building workout. While this exercise may not adequately replace movements like the deadlift, it can perfectly supplement this routine. 
Does using this product contribute to a more focused and efficient quad workout compared to other fitness equipment? 
Squats and deadlifts target the hamstrings and glutes alongside your quads. This machine can take away from maximum quad activation. Leg extensions isolate your quadriceps, ensuring they get the attention needed for increases in strength and size.

Whether you're performing leg extensions or leg curls, this versatile machine supports a complete leg day workout, offering the flexibility to meet individual needs. Ideal for home gyms and commercial fitness spaces, this machine helps you build strength, improve muscle tone, and achieve your fitness goals with ease.
Heavy Duty Leg Extension and Curl Machine with Single Leg Isolation Feature – Maximize Quadriceps and Hamstrings Development 
Step up your leg training with the Heavy Duty Leg Extension and Curl Machine designed to enhance your strength training routine by isolating the quadriceps and hamstrings for maximum muscle growth and definition. Whether you’re aiming to build quad strength, improve hamstring flexibility, or correct muscle imbalances, this plate-loaded leg curl machine delivers the perfect solution. 
With a 330 lb weight capacity, this machine allows you to push your limits and build impressive leg muscles. The single leg extension isolation feature enables users to focus on one leg at a time, promoting symmetry and enhancing strength in both legs individually. This feature is especially beneficial for those recovering from injuries or wanting to address muscle imbalances. The independent leg movement also allows you to target hamstrings and quads with precision, ensuring an effective and tailored workout every time. 
Designed with durability in mind, the dual-layer vinyl padding offers both comfort and support throughout your workout. The thick padding helps reduce strain and discomfort, allowing you to focus on your form and performance. Whether you’re performing leg extensions or leg curls, the padding ensures a smooth and comfortable experience. Plus, the adjustable design allows you to customize the machine to your specific body type, ensuring you maintain proper alignment and posture throughout each movement. 
The Heavy Duty Leg Extension and Curl Machine isn’t just limited to leg extensions or leg curls. Its versatile design allows you to perform a variety of lower body exercises targeting the quadriceps, hamstrings, glutes, and even your calves. You can switch between exercises quickly and easily, focusing on leg curls for hamstring development or leg extensions to isolate the quadriceps for a stronger, more defined lower body. 
By allowing you to work both legs simultaneously or isolating one leg at a time, this machine gives you the flexibility to tailor your workout routine to your goals. For example, single-leg isolation is ideal for rehabilitation exercises or for those looking to correct muscle imbalances between legs. It also aids in unilateral strength development, ensuring equal strength and muscle size in both legs. 
This leg extension machine is built to be compact and space-efficient, making it a perfect addition to any home gym or light-commercial fitness center. Despite its heavy-duty construction, it doesn’t take up a lot of floor space, making it ideal for those with limited workout room. The space-saving design allows you to keep your gym area organized without compromising on performance or functionality. 
Whether you are focusing on muscle development, strength training, or rehabilitation, this leg machine offers a reliable and efficient workout experience. It’s perfect for anyone looking to improve their lower body strength, enhance muscle definition, or address muscle imbalances in the quads and hamstrings. 
With a maximum weight capacity of 330 lbs, this leg machine is built to handle even the most intense weightlifting sessions. Whether you are performing light, high-repetition sets to tone your muscles or heavy sets for muscle mass, this machine can support your needs. The 330 lb weight capacity ensures that you can progressively increase the weight as you advance in your training, making it suitable for a variety of fitness levels, from beginners to advanced lifters. 
Safety and comfort are paramount when performing leg exercises, and this machine delivers both. The adjustable footrests and shin pads ensure proper positioning, while the adjustable thigh support accommodates different body sizes, allowing for a customizable workout. Additionally, the safety stops prevent any accidents if you are unable to complete a lift, ensuring a safe and secure exercise experience every time.

modules.title: Heavy Duty Leg Extension and Curl Machine with Single Leg Isolation Feature – Maximize Quadriceps and Hamstrings Development
modules.text:
Step up your leg training with the Heavy Duty Leg Extension and Curl Machine designed to enhance your strength training routine by isolating the quadriceps and hamstrings for maximum muscle growth and definition. Whether you’re aiming to build quad strength, improve hamstring flexibility, or correct muscle imbalances, this plate-loaded leg curl machine delivers the perfect solution. 
With a 330 lb weight capacity, this machine allows you to push your limits and build impressive leg muscles. The single leg extension isolation feature enables users to focus on one leg at a time, promoting symmetry and enhancing strength in both legs individually. This feature is especially beneficial for those recovering from injuries or wanting to address muscle imbalances. The independent leg movement also allows you to target hamstrings and quads with precision, ensuring an effective and tailored workout every time. 
Designed with durability in mind, the dual-layer vinyl padding offers both comfort and support throughout your workout. The thick padding helps reduce strain and discomfort, allowing you to focus on your form and performance. Whether you’re performing leg extensions or leg curls, the padding ensures a smooth and comfortable experience. Plus, the adjustable design allows you to customize the machine to your specific body type, ensuring you maintain proper alignment and posture throughout each movement. 
The Heavy Duty Leg Extension and Curl Machine isn’t just limited to leg extensions or leg curls. Its versatile design allows you to perform a variety of lower body exercises targeting the quadriceps, hamstrings, glutes, and even your calves. You can switch between exercises quickly and easily, focusing on leg curls for hamstring development or leg extensions to isolate the quadriceps for a stronger, more defined lower body. 
By allowing you to work both legs simultaneously or isolating one leg at a time, this machine gives you the flexibility to tailor your workout routine to your goals. For example, single-leg isolation is ideal for rehabilitation exercises or for those looking to correct muscle imbalances between legs. It also aids in unilateral strength development, ensuring equal strength and muscle size in both legs. 
This leg extension machine is built to be compact and space-efficient, making it a perfect addition to any home gym or light-commercial fitness center. Despite its heavy-duty construction, it doesn’t take up a lot of floor space, making it ideal for those with limited workout room. The space-saving design allows you to keep your gym area organized without compromising on performance or functionality. 
Whether you are focusing on muscle development, strength training, or rehabilitation, this leg machine offers a reliable and efficient workout experience. It’s perfect for anyone looking to improve their lower body strength, enhance muscle definition, or address muscle imbalances in the quads and hamstrings. 
With a maximum weight capacity of 330 lbs, this leg machine is built to handle even the most intense weightlifting sessions. Whether you are performing light, high-repetition sets to tone your muscles or heavy sets for muscle mass, this machine can support your needs. The 330 lb weight capacity ensures that you can progressively increase the weight as you advance in your training, making it suitable for a variety of fitness levels, from beginners to advanced lifters. 
Safety and comfort are paramount when performing leg exercises, and this machine delivers both. The adjustable footrests and shin pads ensure proper positioning, while the adjustable thigh support accommodates different body sizes, allowing for a customizable workout. Additionally, the safety stops prevent any accidents if you are unable to complete a lift, ensuring a safe and secure exercise experience every time.

Why you need TT2S leg extension and curl machine for leg day? 
“Pro"-is the answer. GMWD was shuttled to countless gyms and factories and tested it for over six months. If you want to get more sturdy thighs the right way, choose it. 
What's the latest update point of TT2S? 
GMWD's engineers have changed the way weight holder is attached. Once again, the weighing capacity is increased and structural stability also level up. It's one step closer to the perfect leg day training machine. 
What is the most memorable point in TT2S's design process? 
In order to simultaneously achieve good support for the knees, keep the axis of motion parallel to the knees, and make the equipment accessible to most family members in home gym, engineers has tweaked the statistics for over 1 month. 
Why you should do leg extension and leg curl at home? 
The leg extension and the leg curl are valuable isolation exercises. Leg curls are a valuable addition to your leg-building workout. While this exercise may not adequately replace movements like the deadlift, it can perfectly supplement this routine. 
Does using this product contribute to a more focused and efficient quad workout compared to other fitness equipment? 
Squats and deadlifts target the hamstrings and glutes alongside your quads. This machine can take away from maximum quad activation. Leg extensions isolate your quadriceps, ensuring they get the attention needed for increases in strength and size.

features: Commercial Grade for Home Gym & Garage Gym Use: Strong hamstrings and quadriceps are crucial for balance, speed and coordination. Unique cable and pulley system supplies consistent resistance throughout the motions, which differs from traditional lever operated machine and assists with the growth of stronger and more defined muscles. The pulley with an enhanced steel core can withstand heavier loads and more intensive training. Awesome Addition to Home Gym with Reliable Warranty: The assembled dimension is 45” width x 56” depth x 41” height to fit into your home gym. We offer Manufacturer Limited Warranty: 2 years on framework (structural steel & welds) and 1 year on other parts. Assembly instructions and wrenches will come with the machine. description: leg press/hack squat machine
features: [Compact for Limited Space] The LP10 leg press and hack squat machine, with dimensions of 67 inches (L) x 52 inches (W) x 47 inches (H) and a footprint of only 24.2 sq. m., offers efficient space utilization. Compared to other large combo machines, this machine can save almost 1/3 of the space. The installation manual and video guide you through the assembly quickly. The LP10 is ideal for limited spaces such as a garage or home gym.

[Unique 30°Combo Machine] Unlike the common 45°leg press hack squat combo machine on the market, we offer a unique 30°positive angle. The relaxed 30°position enables better isolation of the quadriceps, and it’s friendly for individuals with insufficient lower back strength and knee joint issues. Compared to traditional squat racks and barbells, it’s generally considered safer and more user-friendly.
[Pocket-Friendly] Save your wallet without compromising the effectiveness of your leg workout.

[Full Range of Motion] Another great feature of the LP10 leg press hack squat combo machine is its full range of motion, which allows you to achieve deeper depth in your squats, even allowing for an ATG squat. Most 45°combo machines have a seat pad installed under the guide rail for users to get support while doing leg press, but this overall squat range is limited. In comparison, the LP10 is definitely a wise choice.

[Easy Adjustable, Easy Organize] The backboard and foot pedals can be adjusted in 7 angles respectively to target different muscle groups. The shoulder pad used for assisting hack squats is removable and has 3 adjustable positions to accommodate people of different heights. We also added a storage area at the back of the product to keep your weight plates organized. The band pegs allow you to use resistance bands for resistance training.

[Stable Construction] The LP10 has excellent stability and smooth performance. The steel tubes of the rails are 3mm thick and very robust. With a maximum weight capacity of 1000 lbs, it's solid and reliable. Our unique stop-loss device, featuring 1 solid stopper and 5 adjustable hole positions, ensures 100% injury prevention. Each stopper can handle a weight of up to 500 lbs.

title: RitFit Leg Press Hack Squat Machine, Professional Adjustable Leg Press Machine for Home Gym with Linear Bearing, Specialty Hack Squat Machine for Full Lower Body Workout with Weight Storage Posts
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Weight Machines › Leg Machines
description: Experience the stability and versatility of our leg press and hack squat machine. Angled at 45 degree, the entire structure ensures a safe and comfortable workout. Target various leg muscles utilizing the dual function of the inclined leg press and hack squat. The wider and thicker cushions are wrapped in high quality leather that is durable and easy to clean, allowing you to enjoy a more comfortable experience. Our machine prioritizes safety with solid guide rods, cushioning pads, and two storage for barbell plates. Adjustable footplate accomodate your body shape, providing an ergonomic exercise experience. Packed separately, we ensure minimal wear and tear during shipping. Expect packages to arrive on different dates, but rest assured as we will keep a close eye on the logistics for you.
features: 【Stability & Versatile Workout】This two-in-one leg press and hack squat machine is adapted linear bearings rather than rolling ones, and it is constructed of heavy-duty high tensile beefy steel. Beyond that, there are two weight plate storage holders at the rear bottom, when stacked up, greatly enhance machine's stability when in motion. By adjusting the placement of your feet on the foot plate, you can focus more on training isolating muscle groups.

【Comfort & Smooth Exercise Experience】This leg press and hack squat gym machine features thick shoulder and backrest cushion wrapped in premium anti-slip and wear-resistant leather surface, providing ultimate and long-lasting comfort to ease your strain and stress, and protecting your bones and joints during your bodybuilding. Solid metal guide rods (sled) and aluminium alloy grips on both sides upgrade your workout experience without jerk motions.

【Safety & Considerate Design】The weight carriage fits 2'' plates, and Max 1200 lbs plate loading satisfies most users' needs. It is beginner-friendly, for experienced pro, you can do one leg at a time. Large diamond-plated footplate increases friction, preventing accidental sideslipping while in use. Two cushionings at the sled's bottom soften sudden impact with less noise. The triangular piece at the base of the back support also enhances overall stability.

【Multiple Adjustments】As a well-crafted design, there are 5 angle choices for hack squat and 3 for leg press setting, accomodating different sized athelets. The side rail (safety catches attached) handles can be pushed out to unlock the sled. After you are done with your set, pull both handles inward yourself to lock the sled in your designated lockout position. With a quick flip of the back pad and lowering of the leg press footplate, you can switch workouts in seconds to perform hack squat.

Product Description
MOST EFFECTIVE ANKLE STRAP PAIR FOR LEG AND GLUTE WORKOUTS 
For shapely legs and a firmer butt, working your glutes is key. Designed especially for kickback exercises, our resistance band ankle straps are made for a more comfortable, and in turn, more effective workout. That means that every time you hit the gym, you’ll be getting the maximum benefit from your workout. Turn it up, feel the burn, and build the booty you’ve always dreamed about! 
Get the most out of every gym visit and work your way to a body that looks great. Whether you’re at the beach, out with the girls, or down at the gym, everyone will envy your slim figure and tight butt! Tone and trim your muscles to build a flawless physique and feel confident about how you look. 
VERSATILE AND MULTIPURPOSE 
An essential gym accessory, our gym ankle strap for cable machine can be used with cable machines, resistance trainers, and other gym equipment. If you’re exercising at home, they’re perfect for adding intensity and support to glute kickbacks, leg extensions, and weight training. 
Use them to warm up your glutes by doing glute kickbacks and side leg raises on the cable machine.Or isolate your quads and hamstrings by doing leg extensions and hamstring curls! 
With these wrist wraps, you’ll instantly realize just what you’ve been missing. 
Our ankle straps are made for you. 
We Are Confident You Will Love Your Ankle Workout Straps! 
What are you waiting for? Start working out now. 
NEOPRENE PADDING, COMFORTABLE WITH ZERO CHAFING 
The lining adds comfort and softness neoprene so that more gently adhere to the skin. 7mm thickness ensures that the force is evenly distributed when you perform each movement. You’ll come away from your workout with no ankle pain whatsoever. 
Our cable machine ankle attachment don’t fray, break, or lose their shape. The velcro is thick, sticks down securely, and is built to last. You can use them for years - our velcro will hold up and keep you on track for a better body and firmer butt. 
FOR A CANFIDENT SAFE WORKOUT 
When you workout, you need to be confident your gear will do the job. Other ankle straps slip, slide, and ride up the leg. That means you’ll constantly need to interrupt your exercise and readjust them. 
HPYGN cable leg attachments for gym are different. Our unique, cleverly designed kickback straps hold the main strap firmly in place, stopping it from sliding up your leg. That means that even if you’re pulling a heavy weight, your straps will grip onto your ankles and never let go - without shifting or chafing. No matter how hard you work out, you can be confident the cable ankle attachments for gym will hold up.

Yes! Designed to keep the ankles comfortable, yet engaged during your sessions, the ankle cups should feel as great for short sessions as they do for long.If you find the pads hard, just add a small cloth to make them even softer. 
How far apart are the ankle cups? 
The cups are spaced just right for most body types, thanks to careful research into the ideal ankle distance for swing machines. 
Is the motor loud while in use? 
While it isn't great for using next to a sleeping baby or partner, the motor is quiet enough for pleasant bedroom use, where you can get the most out of every session. 
Can the MediRipple help me pick up my energy? 
Yes! Some of the settings are meant for invigoration, while others for relaxation. You choose! 
Who can benefit from the MediRipple Swing Machine? 
It's great for people who can't exercise while standing, have high blood pressure, suffer from ankle, foot, or leg pain, and those who spend long hours on their feet. 
12 SWING SPEED SETTINGS 	Adjust your swing intensity from relaxing and slow, to energizing and fast. Each speed brings different benefits - from improved circulation, to lower blood pressure and tension relief. 	
POWERFUL 50 W MOTOR 	Made to last, and always ready to deliver precise swings and vibrations, the powerful motor is both quiet enough for use at home, and powerful enough to help you find relief & accelerated recovery. 	
COMPACT & CONVENIENT 	Easy to store, and easy to use in any bed, the MediRipple is both compact and convenient. Just plug it into the nearest outlet, lay down, and let the swing machine stimulate your wellness. 	
VIBRATION MASSAGE 	Made to enhance lymphatic drainage & improve your stress management, the MediRipple vibrating massage ushers in deep calm & comfort after every use. 	
BUILT-IN INFRARED THERAPY 	Turn on the red light therapy module & enjoy even more beneficial sessions that reach deep into muscle tissues to quickly take care of those pesky pains & tensions.

title: Body-Solid LVLC Leverage Leg Curl Machine with Adjustable Foot Rollers and V-Bench Design – Versatile Home Gym Equipment for Leg Strengthening Workouts
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Weight Machines › Leg Machines
description: The Body-Solid ProClubLine Leverage Leg Curl Machine (LVLC) is designed to give you focused and intense leg workouts with comfort and safety specifically in mind. The uniquely designed V-bench offers total hamstring isolation while helping reduce back stress and unwanted knee forces. A direct link movement arm design and sealed bearing pivot points deliver smooth and continuous range of motion as you lift for an uninterrupted workout.Made with a 2- by 3-inch 11-gauge high-tensile strength steel mainframe and double-stitched upholstery, this calf workout machine is durably constructed to stand up to rigorous use in gyms and clubs. It features side handles for stability and control while you workout, with fully adjustable foot rollers to fit users of all sizes. Weight plate holders are built into the machine for easy storage (plates sold separately).When assembled, the Body-Solid ProClubLine Leverage Leg Curl Machine measures 74 by 46 by 26 inches (L x W x H) and weighs145 pounds. It is backed by the Body-Solid Lifetime In-Home Warranty and Full Commercial Warranty.
features: INDUSTRY LEADER: For 30+ years, Body Solid has held the widest array of products designed to meet the demands of the ever-changing fitness industry (home gym, free weight machines, treadmills, bikes, ellipticals, weight plates, kettlebells, dumbbells, flooring, accessories and more). Our products are cutting edge and reliable and are built for Life……Your Life.

DURABLE AND COMFORTABLE: This Leg Curl machine features durable, double-stitched upholstery that ensures comfort during intense workouts. The sealed bearing pivot points and adjustable foot rollers accommodate all user sizes, making it an ideal choice for any home gym.

SMOOTH AND ADJUSTABLE PERFORMANCE: This Leg Curl machine is engineered with a direct link movement arm design for a smooth lifting experience, while the adjustable foot rollers accommodate various user heights, ensuring a personalized workout for maximum muscle engagement.

VERSATILE LEG WORKOUTS: This exercise machine is perfect for targeting hamstrings with its V-bench design for total hamstring isolation and adjustable foot rollers. This versatile leg workout machine ensures reduced back stress and unwanted knee forces, making it an essential addition to any home gym.

DIMENSIONS: This Leg Curl machine is crafted with a robust 11-gauge steel frame and an attractive metallic silver powder coat finish, ensuring longevity and a professional look in your home gym. Measures 74"x46"x26" and weighs 165lbs.

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
Previous page
Next page
Why you need LE02 leg extension and curl machine for leg day? 
“Pro"-is the answer. GMWD was shuttled to countless gyms and factories and tested it for over six months. If you want to get more sturdy thighs the right way, choose it. LE02 leg extension machine is the best value for money. 
What is the most memorable point in LE02's design process? 
In order to simultaneously achieve good support for the knees, keep the axis of motion parallel to the knees, and make the equipment accessible to most family members in home gym, engineers has tweaked the statistics for over 1 month. 
What's the latest update point of LE02? 
You can change the leg extension machine to the leg curl machine with a simple plug. The removable thigh holder creates more training possibilities. 
Why you should do leg extension and leg curl at home? 
The leg extension and the leg curl are valuable isolation exercises. Leg curls are a valuable addition to your leg-building workout. While this exercise may not adequately replace movements like the deadlift, it can perfectly supplement this routine. 
Does using this leg machine contribute to a more focused and efficient quad workout compared to other fitness equipment? 
Squats and deadlifts target the hamstrings and glutes alongside your quads. This machine can take away from maximum quad activation. Leg extensions isolate your quadriceps, ensuring they get the attention needed for increases in strength and size.
